title: David Lindley & El Rayo-X - Win This Record!
description:
David Lindley & El Rayo-X - Win This Record! (EAC+FLAC)

1989 European CD issue (probably the same mastering as original US CD issue)

David's second solo album. A really nice record!

3  Spodie

10 Look So Good
